
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>投稿完了</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Rubik:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Rubik', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #f0fff0, #d0f5d0);
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      height: 100vh;
    }

    .success-box {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 30px 20px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      text-align: center;
      animation: fadeIn 1s ease-in-out;
      width: 90%;
      max-width: 400px;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    .success-box h1 {
      font-size: 24px;
      color: #2e8b57;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .success-box p {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #444;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
    }

    .return-link {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background-color: #2e8b57;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      border-radius: 8px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s;
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .return-link:hover {
      background-color: #256f47;
    }

    .sns-section {
      margin-top: 30px;
    }

    .sns-message {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #666;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .sns-links {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .sns-links a {
      font-size: 18px;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #444;
      font-weight: bold;
      transition: transform 0.2s, color 0.3s;
    }

    .sns-links a:hover {
      transform: scale(1.2);
      color: #e91e63;
    }

    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="success-box">
    <h1>✅ 投稿が完了しました！</h1>
    <p>あなたのコメントは正常に投稿されました。</p>
    <a class="return-link" href="/threads/<%= threadId %>">スレッドに戻る</a>

    <div class="sns-section">
      <div class="sns-message">良かったらSNSもフォローしてね👇</div>
      <div class="sns-links">
        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/riku0128123" target="_blank" title="Instagram">📷 Instagram</a>
        <a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@riku6701" target="_blank" title="TikTok">🎵 TikTok</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
